    "date": "2021-09-24T15:59:45Z",
    "text": "Investor Choice Act of 2021\n\nThis bill prohibits broker-dealers and investment advisers from including mandatory arbitration, forum selection restrictions, or bans on class action suits in a customer or client agreement. Issuers of securities are also prohibited from mandating arbitration in a shareholder agreement."
